## Maintenance

When you add, remove, or rename a file in this folder, update **all three indexes**:

1. `CLAUDE.md` reference table at the project root
2. `AGENTS.md` reference table at the project root
3. The skill (in `.agents/skills/` or `.claude/skills/`) that points to this doc
4. Any nested `AGENTS.md` files that reference it
5. The file table above

The `writing-docs.md` file has the canonical maintenance checklist.
